{"tid":1120932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大嶼山60歲單車男自炒 頭傷送院","createTime":"2019-04-23T04:18:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-23T04:35:25.000Z","uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bb8014631102c7d00b72e12dbcb1b63c86818bc4","tid":1120932,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T04:18:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N32n6ne.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN32n6ne.png&h=8b458c65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n單車男頭傷送院。詹家志攝<br />\n<br />\n大嶼山羗山道近石壁，早上9時21分，一名年約60歲男村民踩單車返家途中，其間失平衡跌落單車，額頭、臉及手腳擦傷，男途人見狀為他報警求助，事主清醒送往瑪嘉烈醫院治理，警方正調查事件。"},{"pid":"71e3817c560ca2724da3d3489da4920257471957","tid":1120932,"uid":95108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T04:35:25.000Z","msg":"下下都去瑪嘉烈 究竟北大嶼山醫院既用途係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}